ayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":25901,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: Listening to the Prophet\u2019s night prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Rabi\u2019ah ibn Ka\u2019b reported: I stayed the night by the door of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, to give him water for ablution. I heard him saying throughout the night, \u201cAllah hears those who praise Him,\u201d and I heard him saying, \u201cPraise be to Allah, the Lord\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1738,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/08\/allah-you-are-as-praised-yourself\/","url_meta":{"origin":25901,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hamd: O Allah, You are as You praised Yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: One night in bed, I missed the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, so I looked for him and my hand touched his feet while he was in prostration. They were raised, and the Prophet was saying, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in Your pleasure\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33170,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/what-imam-says-in-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":25901,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: What the Imam and followers say in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah heard those who praise him,\u201d he would say, \u201cO Allah, our Lord, for you is praise.\u201d When the Prophet bowed and raised his head, he would declare the greatness of Allah. When he stood from the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/prophet-asks-nur-noor\/","url_meta":{"origin":25901,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet asks Allah for light in his heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: He spent the night with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he woke up. The Prophet cleansed his teeth, performed ablution, the call to prayer was announced, and he went out for the prayer while he was saying, \u201cO Allah, place light\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13564,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/13\/gates-paradise-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":25901,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Supplication for purity after ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs ablution in the best manner and he says, 'I bear witness there is no God but Allah alone, without any partners, and I bear witness that Muhammad is His servant and His Messenger.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25554,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/06\/dua-qiyam-al-layl-takbir\/","url_meta":{"origin":25901,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet&#8217;s night prayer routine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Shariq al-Hawzani reported: I entered the home of Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, and I asked her, \u201cHow did the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, begin his prayer when he awakened at night?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen the Prophet awakened at night, he would exalt\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25901","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25901"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/